[SN]TITLE[SN]
Logan Tomkins: Salford Red Devils sign Wigan Warriors hooker

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Salford Red Devils have signed hooker Logan Tomkins on a permanent basis from Wigan Warriors.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Tomkins, 23, will remain at the Red Devils for the 2016 season, after loan spells in 2014 and 2015.
He made 15 appearances last term, having also played 38 career games for the Warriors following his 2012 debut.
"Delighted that Logan Tomkins is now a Salford Red Devil. Great addition to the team," owner Dr Marwan Koukash tweeted about the signing.
